summary: This appears to be an email forwarding Palm Beach police reports to an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York, referencing calls made by an unidentified female subject and a threat.

persons.name: Assistant United States Attorney
persons.context: Recipient of an email containing Palm Beach police reports regarding calls and a threat made by an unidentified female subject.

locations: One Saint Andrew's Plaza, New York, NY 10007
keyFacts: Palm Beach police reports were forwarded to a federal prosecutor in New York on October 15, 2019.
The reports concern calls made by an unidentified female subject and a threat she made.
The first page of the attached reports addresses the threat, while later pages contain call records from around that time.
